commands.desc-config:
- **/role add** - Add roles to users.
- **/role remove** - Remove roles from users.
- **/role mute** - Add for mutes.
 - **/setchannel** - Sets a channel.
- **/welcome** - Enable/Disabled the welcome system.
commands.desc-fun:
- **/8ball** - Ask a question and it will give you an answer.
 - **/avatar** - Show your avatar or that of another user.
- **/weather** - Give you the weather the place you want.
- **/dice** - Gives a random number.
- **/achievement** - Shows a minecraft logo with the text you want.
commands.desc-eco:
- **/work** - You work and earn money.
- **/beg** - You beg so you can earn some money.
- **/balance** - You check your wallet and bank account. 
- **/pay** - Give money to your friends.
- **/daily** - Claim daily rewards.
- **/steal** - You can steal from another user.
 - **/crime** - You commit a crime to earn money.
 - **/deposit** - You deposit money in the bank.
- **/withdraw** - Withdraw money from the bank.
 - **/give** - Give money to users.
- **/rest** - Take money from users.
 - **/postvideo** - Post a video on a social network.
- ** /postmeme** - Post a meme on a social network.
commands.desc-info:
- **/commands** - Show all Life commands.
- **/poll** - Conduct polls for users.
 - **/invite** - Invite the bot to your server.
 - **/roles** - Shows all server roles.
 - **/server** - Gives server information.
 - **/status** - Current Life stats.
- ** /suggest** - Make a suggestion for the server.
 - **/uptime** - Tells the uptime of the bot.
 - **/user** - Gives user information.
commands.desc-inte:
- **/hug** - Give hugs to the user.
 - **/kiss** - Give the user a kiss.
 - **/happy** - Express happiness.
- **/cry** - Express sadness.
- **/pat** - Pat a user.
- **/sleep** - Express that they are sleepy.
 - **/blush** - Express that you are blushing.
 - **/bonk** - You receive a bonk.
- **/confused** - Express that you are confused.
- **/feed** - Feed another user.
- **/dance** - Dance for life.
- **/slap** - Slap a user on the face.
- **/suicide** - Express suicide.
commands.desc-mine:
- **/bag** - Shows all the items you have saved.
- **/buy mining** - You buy items/tools in the market.
- **/minar** - Mines with the pickaxe that choose.
- **/repair** - Repair the chosen pickaxe.
- **/sell** - Sell the ores.
- **/shop mining** - Check the market.
commands.desc-level:
- **/level on** - Activates the level system.
- **/level off** - Deactivates the level system.
- **/leaderboard** - Checks the ranking of the levels.
- **/rank** - See your level on the server.
commands.desc-setup:
- **/setup cooldown** - Set job cooldown.
- **/setup currency** - Set economy emoji.
 - **/setup payout** - Set payout jobs.
commands.desc-give:
- **/start** - Start a draw.
- **/reroll** - Choose another winner.
commands.desc-music:
- **/autoplay** - Random music from your playlist.
- **/back** - Play the previous song.
 - **/nowplaying** - Toggle playlist autoplay.
- **/pause** - Pause the current song.
- **/play song** - Play a song.
 - **/queue** - Show the playlist.
 - **/resume** - Start paused music.
 - ** /skip** - Skip songs.
 - **/stop** - Stop the music.
- **/volume** - Set the volume of music
commands.desc-mod:
- **/slowmode** - Sets slow mode.
- **/lock** - Locks a channel.
 - **/unlock** - Unlocks a channel.
- **/clear** - Delete messages.
- **/ban** - Ban a user.
- **/unban** - Unban a user.
- **/kick** - Kick a user.
- **/warn add** - Add a warning to a user.
- **/warn check** - Check warnings to a user.
- **/warn remove** - Remove a warning to a user.
- **/warn clear** - Clear all warnings to a user.
